<html> <head><TITLE>Dance</TITLE></head><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
SUNY Potsdam<BR>

<IMG  Align=Right SRC="../gif/Virtual_Library.gif"><H1><CENTER>Dance</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<!-- DO NOT CHANGE PAGE NAME>


<A HREF = "http://www.yahoo.com/Entertainment/Dance/">Dance</A> - links from the Yahoo directory at Stanford<P>

<A HREF="http://www.nypl.org/research/lpa/dan/dan.html">Catalog of the Dance Collection at the New York Public Library</A>: choose "Catalogs", and use "CATNYP".<BR>
The Research Libraries' Dance Collection catalog has been added to CATNYP. The data is fully
integrated in CATNYP, so a search using any index will retrieve Dance Collection records when
appropriate. If you wish to limit your searching exclusively to the Dance Collection you will have
to use "telnet" access to CATNYP through 149.123.1.2 (nyplgate.nypl.org). When you address
CATNYP through that interface, you may limit your searching exclusively to DANCE by selecting
from the index menu: y> Change Scope of Database Then, choose "Dance Collection" as your
default. 
<P>


<A HREF = "http://www.weblink.com/nyibc/Events/events.html">Calendar of dance events</A><P>

<A HREF="http://bohr.physics.purdue.edu/~jswhite/dance_links.html">Dance Links Web site at Purdue University</A>,<dd>
compiled mainly from information provided by dance videographer Amy Reusch, includes the University Dance Departments pointers page, a collection of pointers to over 150 U.S. University Dance departments, as well as
departments in Australia, Canada, Finland, Ireland, and the United Kingdom. Dance Links also points to resources related to dance companies, performance listings, publications, organizations, funding, dance schools, dancers, and other dance indexes.<P>



<A HREF="http://www.ens-lyon.fr/~esouche/danse/dance.html">Dance Pages</A>:  dance sites and dance history<P>
<A HREF="http://www.pbs.org:80/dancing/dancinghome.html/">Dancing:</A>  the PBS video series (1993)<P>


<HR noshade>
<CENTER><A HREF="DanceHome.html">Dance Department HomePage</A></CENTER><P>


<A HREF="../connections.html"><IMG  Align=Top SRC="../gif/paw.gif">To BearFacts main menu</A><P>
