<FONT SIZE=4><BR><B>Thank you </B></FONT> for taking a moment as you cruise along the Internet to stop by.   I am currently the Coordinator for Institutional Research at the State University of New York College at Potsdam..  The Institutional Research Office is a single person office staffed by me (Peter Hoyt).  <BR><BR>


I am the father of two great kids (Tom and <A HREF = "Alicia.gif">Alicia</A>) and husband to my best friend and a wonderful lady (Cheryl). Our home is located in the country.
  As you can see I am a person who loves the outdoors and more specifically the <A HREF = "http://www.adirondack.net/adnet/adnet.html">Adirondack Mountains of New York State</A>.  On those rare occasions I get a day off you might find me fishing at one of the remote <A HREF="lakeLila.gif">lakes</A>, rivers or <A HREF = "Stream.gif">streams</A> of the Adirondack Mountains.  My hobbies include camping, fishing, and canoeing.
<BR><BR>
Please feel free to linger here as long as you like.  I would offer you a cup of coffee if I knew how to get it across the internet.  If you have any questions or suggestions please feel free to drop me an <a href=mailto:hoytpj@potsdam.edu>Email</a> or give me a call on the phone.

<BR><H4>Please, Enjoy your visit!</H4>
<BR>
