<IMG WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32  SRC="logo-red.GIF"></CENTER><P>

<center><H1><font color="#000050">W<FONT SIZE=4>ILLIAM</FONT> C. M<FONT SIZE=4>ERWIN</FONT><BR>
R<FONT SIZE=4>URAL</FONT> S<FONT SIZE=4>ERVICES</FONT> I<FONT SIZE=4>NSTITUTE</FONT></font></CENTER></h1><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=6>M</FONT><FONT SIZE=5>UNICIPAL </FONT><FONT SIZE=6>G</FONT><FONT SIZE=5>ARAGE </FONT><FONT SIZE=6>S</FONT><FONT SIZE=5>ALE</FONT></CENTER><P>
<!-- Horizontal Line Tag -->
<HR WIDTH=100%><P>
<FONT SIZE=4>The Muncipal Garage Sale Directory is a compilation of items for sale, exchange, or trade among local governments in Franklin, Jefferson, Lewis, and St. Lawrence Counties.  If you have items to advertise, you can submit them below.  The William C. Merwin Rural Services Institute will edit all material submitted for publication in the Municipal Garage Sale Directory.  The next issue will be published in March, 1997.  All ads must be received by <B>March 1, 1997</B>.<P>

