http://www.potsdam.edu:80/PSYC/HearSciCourses.html 137.143.111.2 19970208222333 text/html 3969
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/31205
Message-ID: <af0d121d.143049@www.potsdam.edu>
