<DOCHDR>
http://www.potsdam.edu:80/hr/HRHomePage/Holidays96 137.143.111.2 19970209020312 text/html 5151
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/31205
Message-ID: <af0d121d.144953@www.potsdam.edu>
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 20:58:02 GMT
