<DOCHDR>
http://www.potsdam.edu:80/hr/HRHomePage/Vacancies/Prof.Adm.Positions/Counselor 137.143.111.2 19970209021857 text/html 1157
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/31205
Message-ID: <af0d121d.145079@www.potsdam.edu>
