<HEAD><TITLE>Untitled</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY> 
SUNY Potsdam invites applications for a temporary one year position for the 1997-98 academic year as Visiting Assistant Professor of  US History.  Responsibilities are to teach US history and history in a non-Western field.  MA  required, PhD preferred.  Send letter of application, resume, and three current letters of reference to Dr. Arthur Johnson, History Dept., SUNY Potsdam, Potsdam, NY 13676.  Closing date for receipt of applications is March 21, 1997.  SUNY Potsdam is an equal employment opportunity affirmative action employer committed to excellence through diversity.
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

January 1997


