<HTML> 
<HEAD><TITLE>MACINTOSH: Selecting a Student-Usable Laserprinter</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"> 
<IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="http://www.potsdam.edu/DCTM/DCTMlogo.gif"><HR>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER><TR>
<TH><A HREF="/PotsdamHome.html"><IMG  SRC="/navigation/gif/buttons/homepage.GIF"></a></TH>
<TH><A HREF="/helpdesk/HELPDESKrequest-form.html"><IMG  SRC="/navigation/gif/buttons/help.GIF"></a></th>
 <TH><A HREF="StudLaserPrintingfeedback.html"><IMG  SRC="/navigation/gif/buttons/feedback.GIF"></a></TH>
<TH><A HREF="/helpdesk/filecabinet.html"><IMG  SRC="/navigation/gif/buttons/helpdesk.GIF"></A></TH>
</TD></TABLE></CENTER><HR>

<FONT SIZE=5><B><CENTER>Selecting a laserprinter<BR>
(which students may print to)<BR>
on the network</CENTER></B></FONT><P>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=4>1. Select CHOOSER from the Apple menu.</FONT><P>
<CENTER><!-- Graphic Tag --><IMG WIDTH=216 HEIGHT=241  SRC="GetChooser.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<!-- Horizontal Line Tag --><HR WIDTH=50% SIZE=4 ALIGN=Center NOSHADE>
<P>

<FONT SIZE=4>2. Select (highlight) the LaserWriter icon (such as the Levitt Center in the AppleTalk Zones, and the name of the printer - Levitt LaserWriter in Crumb Library or Levitt LaserWriter in Carson).</FONT><P>
<!-- Graphic Tag --><IMG WIDTH=464 HEIGHT=313  SRC="SelectLaserprinter.gif">
<P>
<!-- Horizontal Line Tag --><HR WIDTH=50% SIZE=4 ALIGN=Center NOSHADE>
<P>

<FONT SIZE=4>3. Then, click the close box on the Chooser.</FONT><P>
<!-- Graphic Tag --><IMG WIDTH=464 HEIGHT=313  SRC="CloseChooser.gif">
<P>
<!-- Horizontal Line Tag --><HR WIDTH=50% SIZE=4 ALIGN=Center NOSHADE>
<P>

<FONT SIZE=4><B>Note:</B><BR>
To select Imagewriter printers, select the <I>AppleTalk...geWriter</I>  icon from the Chooser and make selections similar to the process shown above for selecting a LaserWriter.</FONT><P>
<P><P>


</BODY> 
<HR>
<i>Last Modified: 5/23/96</i><br>
Contact: R. Jewett (email:  <a href=mailto:jewettrj@potsdam.edu>jewettrj@potsdam.edu</a>

