<html><head><title>Middle School</title></head><body><H1><CENTER>TEACHER EDUCATION - MIDDLE
SCHOOL</CENTER></H1><p>
<HR>
<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=5><B>(315) 267-2535   &#183;       Email to: <a href=mailto:mlynarhc@potsdam.edu>Teacher Education</a> </B></FONT>
