<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><!-- Anchor Point Tag --><A NAME="Welcome to the SUNY Potsdam Human Resources Home Page">Welcome to the SUNY Potsdam Human Resources Home Page</A>.<BR>
This site contains information of interest to employees of the college.</FONT></B>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="TopicsOfInterest.html">Topics of Interest</A></FONT>
<BLOCKQUOTE>This area contains current announcements, updated information on policies, procedures, payments, and other topics of interest including increasing your retirement savings through tax sheltered annuities, social security and medicare deductions, New York State Holidays .</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BLINK><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4>"New" Items</FONT></BLINK><BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="disneyclub">Walt Disney's Magic Kingdom Club</A><BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="Benefits.html">Employee Benefits</A></FONT>
<BLOCKQUOTE>This area contains updated information on health insurance, dental care, vision care, prescription drugs, retirement programs, and other benefits including tax shelters, as well as important health and other benefit telehone numbers.</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="Payroll.html">Payroll</A></FONT>
<BLOCKQUOTE>This area contains updated information about agency fees, payroll deductions, direct deposit, time and attendance, state holidays, salary schedules, withholding and other information related to payroll.<BR>
<BR>
Future additions will include: payroll policies and procedures, payroll calendars, and pay check distribution procedures.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><!-- Link Tag -->Handbooks</FONT>
<BLOCKQUOTE>This area contains the <!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="../faculty_handbook/home.html">Faculty Handbook</A> and Employee Handbooks.  Contained in the handbooks are policies and procedures for SUNY Potsdam employees.</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="Vacancies/VacanciesIndex.html">Vacancies</A></FONT>
<BLOCKQUOTE>This area contains the position vacancies for SUNY Potsdam.  The vacancies are divided into three categories: Classified Service (clerical, maintenance, and public safety), Faculty Positions, and Professional and Administrative Positions.</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="Factbook.html">Fact Book</A></FONT>
<BLOCKQUOTE>This area contains statistical information about the faculty and staff at SUNY Potsdam.</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<BR>
<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www2.potsdam.edu/DCTM/luciacb/EAP.html"><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=4>Employee Assistance Program</A></FONT><BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>This area contains information regarding library materials, brochures and contacts.</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<BR>


<FONT SIZE=4>Forms</FONT>
