<dl>
<dt>These are good GUIDES to career and job resources and sites on the internet.  Use these to browse around for other listings. <P><A HREF = "http://rescomp.stanford.edu/jobs.html">Stanford Online Job Service</A>

<dt><A HREF ="http://wings.buffalo.edu/employment/cdo/">SUNY Career Development Organization Homepage</A>

<dt><A HREF = "http://amsquare.com/america/registry.html"> Internet Resume Services </A>:  <dd> Collected Guides to Resume Services on the Internet. 

<dt><A HREF ="http://www.nova.edu/Inter-Links/employment.html">Nova Univ. - Florida Employment Resources</A> 

<dt><A HREF ="">Riley's Job Guide</A> 

<dt><A HREF ="http://www.jobweb.org/CATAPULT/catapult.HTM">Catapult of JobWeb</A>

<dt><A HREF = "http://www.umanitoba.ca/counselling/careers.html">Guides to Career Information</A>: <dd>


</dl>
