<DOCHDR>
http://www.potsdam.edu:80/EDUC/GLC/river/math/mathJour 137.143.111.2 19970209021311 text/html 8731
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/31205
Message-ID: <af0d121d.145060@www.potsdam.edu>
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 21:08:01 GMT
