<BR><p><br>

<center><H1>-- 1997 --</H1></CENTER>




<H2>Brown-Bag Technology Sessions --</h2><P>

For presentations and demonstrations of emerging technologies as well as current campus technologies, join us each Thursday at 11:30 in Carson 101* for our brown-bag technology-sharing sessions.<P>
*unless a different location is specified in the announcement.<BR><P>
<DD>      <A HREF = "brownbags/brownbags97.html">1997 Brown-bag Technology Sharing sessions</A>

<BR><P>
<hr><Br>
<H2>Macintosh-based workshops --</H2>

<DD><B>Spring '97 Schedule:</B> <A HREF="Spring97workshops/MACworkshops0197.html">Macintosh training sessions</A>	<I>(Note: nothing scheduled as 1/10/97)</I>

<BR><P><P>

<H2>Windows-based workshops --</H2>

<DD><B>Spring '97 Schedule:</B> <A HREF="Spring97workshops/Win-workshops0197.html">Windows training sessions</A> <I>(Note: nothing scheduled as 1/10/97)</I>

<BR><P>

<HR size=4>
<P>

<B><FONT SIZE=5>Off - Campus Presentations:</FONT></B><P>
<DD><I>Upcoming</I> SUNY Technology Conference (June, <B>1997</B>)<BR><BR>
<DD><A HREF="off-campus/helpdesk/default.html">"SUNY Technology Helpdesk"</A> - SUNY Technology Conference (June, <B>1996</B>)<BR><BR>

<BR><P>
<HR>
<BR>
<h2><A HREF="OLD-training.html">Past workshops/presentations/Brown-bags</A></h2><BR><P>
<HR>
<P>


For more information on information technology-based workshops and presentations, send email to "<B><a href=mailto:helpdesk@potsdam.edu>helpdesk</A></B>".<br><p>

To offer suggestions for future topics, please send your suggestions, and tell us what you think of this page, by clicking on the "<B>Feedback</B>" button above...<BR>
