<!-- Feedback form created by B. Jewett 8/14/95 (email:  jewettrj@potsdam.edu)>

<!-- for this form to work the following fields are required>
<!-- destination, subject, message>



<FORM ACTION="http://www.cgi.potsdam.edu/eudora.acgi" METHOD="POST">

<INPUT NAME="Destination" value="jewettrj@potsdam.edu" TYPE="hidden">
<INPUT NAME="sender" value="feedback@potsdam.edu" TYPE="hidden">

<!-- this is where you would put the sender address if needed>
<!-- by default the sender address is webmaster@potsdam.edu>
<!-- if you change this then you must set Name="sender" for it to work>

<INPUT NAME="Subject" value="Feedback on the IntroTraining.html document" TYPE="hidden">
<INPUT NAME="Message" value="The following information was sent from our [www.potsdam.edu] Web server using the Documentation Feedback Form from the IntroTraining.html document." TYPE="hidden">

<CENTER><H1>What do you think of this</CENTER>
<CENTER>Web Page?</H1></CENTER>
<br><hr><br>
<CENTER><I><B><FONT SIZE=5>We'd like to know!</FONT></B></I>
<h2>Would you take a moment to share your opinions and comments with us by completing this form? </H2></CENTER>
<br><hr><br><p>

When you're finished, just click on the button that says, "<B>SEND feedback</B>".   That's all there is to it!<P>

Right after you click on the <B>SEND feedback</B>, you will see a copy of the message that you are sending to us with our email system. As you will see, your feedback is completely anonymous--no names or usercodes appear anywhere on the message you send us.<p><p>
<I><B><CENTER><FONT SIZE=5>Thanks!</FONT></CENTER></B></I>
<p>
<hr>
<p>
<B>What was your overall opinion of this page?</B><p>
<INPUT TYPE="Radio" NAME="Overall opinion" VALUE="Very useful">Very useful<br>
<INPUT TYPE="Radio" NAME="Overall opinion" VALUE="Somewhat useful">Somewhat useful<br>
<INPUT TYPE="Radio" NAME="Overall opinion" VALUE="Could be useful if changed">Could be useful if changed (Please suggest changes in the "<B>Comments</B>" window below)<br>
<INPUT TYPE="Radio" NAME="Overall opinion" VALUE="Not very useful">Not very useful<br>
<INPUT TYPE="Radio" NAME="Overall opinion" VALUE="Not useful at all">Not useful at all<br><p>

<b>Comments</b><br>
<TEXTAREA  NAME="Comments" ROWS=10 COLS=70>Enter your comments here... Tell us what you think! </TEXTAREA>
<br><p><p>

<B>Tell us a little about you:</B><p>
<INPUT TYPE="Radio" NAME="Type of user" VALUE="Student">Student<br>
<INPUT TYPE="Radio" NAME="Type of user" VALUE="Faculty">Faculty<br>
