<CENTER><H1>Macintosh Training Sessions</H1></CENTER>
<center><B><FONT SIZE=5>Spring '97 schedule</FONT></B></CENTER><br>

<HR SIZE=4>
<p>

<p>
We are trying to put together a schedule of sessions, but have <I>no</I> workshops scheduled at this time (1/9/97).  Please check with the Continuing Education office for possible workshops they may be offering (<B>267-2167</B> or <B>800-458-1142</B>)<P>
<hr>
<P>
