<CENTER><H1>Macintosh Training Sessions</H1></CENTER>
<center><B><FONT SIZE=5>Fall 96 schedule</FONT></B></CENTER><br>

<HR SIZE=4>
<p>


The Macintosh training sessions will be held as follows:<P>

<H2>How to use Email and surf the Internet</H2>
<B>Kellas Computer Classroom</B> (<A HREF="http://www.potsdam.edu/dctm/cybertour-it/kellas/kellas100b.html">Kellas 100B</A>)<BR>
<DL>
<B>12:00 - 12:50pm:</B>
<DD><B>Mondays</B> - 9/16/96, 9/23/96, 9/30/96<P>
<DD><B>Wednesdays</B> - 9/18/96, 9/25/96, 10/2/96
</DL>
<P>
<DL>
<B>7:00 - 8:00pm:</B>
<DD><B>Mondays</B> - 9/16/96, 9/23/96, 9/30/96<P>
<DD><B>Tuesdays</B> - 9/17/96, 9/24/96, 10/1/96
</DL>
<BR>
<P>

<H2>Creating a document in Microsoft Word for Macintosh</H2>
<B>Carson Computer Classroom</B> (<A HREF="http://www.potsdam.edu/dctm/cybertour-it/carson/carson101.html">Carson 101</A>)<BR>

<DL>
<B>12:00 - 12:50pm:</B>
<DD><B>Tuesdays</B> - 9/17/96, 9/24/96, 10/1/96<P>
