<HTML> 
<HEAD><TITLE>Web Training Sessions for Faculty-Staff Members</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#C1FFFF"> 

<FORM ACTION="http://www.cgi.potsdam.edu/eudora.acgi" METHOD="POST">

<INPUT NAME="Destination" value="uphamje@potsdam.edu" TYPE="hidden">
<INPUT NAME="sender" value="helpdesk@potsdam.edu" TYPE="hidden">


<INPUT NAME="Subject" value="Web Training Sessions for SUNY Potsdam Faculty-Staff Members" TYPE="hidden">


<B><CENTER><FONT SIZE=5>Web Training Sessions for<BR>
SUNY Potsdam Faculty-Staff Members</FONT></CENTER></B><BR>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5>Carson 101<BR>
Wednesdays -- 9 to 10 AM and 3 to 4 PM</FONT><BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>PLEASE NOTE: Available space in each session is limited to 12 so register early and call if you will be unable to attend.</FONT></CENTER><BR>

<B>Name:</B> <INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="Name" SIZE=30><BR>
<B>Department</B> <INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="Department" SIZE=30><BR>
<B>Campus Phone #:</B>  <INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="Phone" SIZE=7><BR>
<B>Email address:</B> <INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="Email" SIZE=8><B>@potsdam.edu</B>

<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4>Session 1 - Overview of the World Wide Web:  what there is there, what may be coming, and why everyone is flocking to surf in this cyberspace!<BR>

