<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Helpdesk - How did it work?</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="PotsdamLogo.gif" WIDTH="66" HEIGHT="81" ALIGN="MIDDLE"
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><IMG SRC="Header2.gif" WIDTH="432" HEIGHT="72" ALIGN=
"MIDDLE" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><IMG SRC="PotsdamLogo.gif" WIDTH="66" HEIGHT=
"81" ALIGN="MIDDLE" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
<BR>
<HR SIZE="10"></CENTER>
<H1><CENTER>How did it work for 95-96?</CENTER>
</H1>
<H2>First 2 weeks were great customer satisfaction<BR>
Student workers needed more training / supervision<BR>
Don't try on going, part-time professional support<BR>
Hotline (phone) did not work</H2>
<H1><CENTER>What would we change?</CENTER>
</H1>
<H2>Track Requests<BR>
Get Feedback from Customers<BR>
Fulltime Professional Support Staff<BR>
1 Location and 1 Phone # to Consolidate</H2>
</BODY>
</HTML>
