<CENTER><H1>Please send us feedback on our workshops</H1></CENTER>
<br><hr><br>
Do you want more workshops offered?  Do you want us to offer other types of sessions than the ones described above.  <P>
<CENTER><I><B><FONT SIZE=5>Please let us know!</FONT></B></I>
<HR>
<h2>Would you take a moment to share your opinions and comments with us by completing this form? </H2></CENTER>
<br><hr><br><p>

When you're finished, just click on the button that says, "<B>SEND feedback</B>".   That's all there is to it!<P>

