<DT> Completion of the College's foreign language 	requirement
</DL>
<p>
<b>Recommended courses for 7-12 science program:</b><p>
Biology majors - one physics course and one geology course<BR>

Chemistry majors - one biology course and one geology course<BR>

Geology majors - Astronomy, Meteorology and Genetics<BR>

Physics majors - one biology course and one geology course<p>
<HR>

<b>7-12 SOCIAL STUDIES</b><p>
<DL><DT> (Anthropology, Economics, History, Politics <b><i>or</i> </b>Sociology Major)
