<BR>
<CENTER><strong>IV.  FACULTY COMPENSATION</strong></CENTER> 
	<dt><br><BR>
<BR>

<dd><dl>
<dt><strong>H.  <!-- Anchor Point Tag --><A NAME="EMPLOYER-SPONSORED INDIVIDUAL RETIREMENT ACCOUNT (IRA)">EMPLOYER-SPONSORED INDIVIDUAL RETIREMENT ACCOUNT (IRA)</A></strong> 
<dt>
<dd><dl>
</dl>
<dt><br>
<dd><dl>
