<dt><br>
An Individual Retirement Account (IRA) is available for members of the Professional Services Negotiating Unit (UUP) offered through the AETNA Life Insurance and Annuity Corporation pursuant to Article 37 of the Agreement via payroll deduction.  
</dl>
</dl>
