<dt><strong>K.	<A NAME="4K">UNITED STATES SAVINGS BONDS</A></strong>
<dt><br>
	Any member of the professional staff may elect to join the U.S. Savings Bond program on campus by signing a bond authorization card which may be obtained from the Office of Human Resources.  Deductions are taken from the paycheck for the purchase of the savings bonds.

