<HEAD><TITLE>Chapter 2 J</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#0000ff" vlink="#ff00ff">

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=462 HEIGHT=87  SRC="../FACBOOK.GIF"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><B>II.   FACULTY APPOINTMENT AND EMPLOYMENT</B></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>

<dt>
<A NAME="j"><b>J.	TRANSFER RIGHTS</A></b>
<dt><br>
	Employees covered by the Agreement who desire to transfer to vacancies in other colleges within the University will be given consideration for such vacancies.  Employees whose services are satisfactory but who are terminated through no fault of their own shall be given special consideration for appointment to available positions in other colleges.  Article 34 of the Agreement details the transfer rights.
<dt><br>
Vacancy notices from other SUNY Colleges and elsewhere are regularly posted on the Human Resources' Bulletin Board in the corridor leading from Carson Hall to Raymond Hall and also are available in the UUP Chapter Office on campus as well as on the internet at <!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="../../HRHomePage/Vacancies/VacanciesIndex.html">http://www.potsdam.edu/hr/HRhomepage/Vacancies/VacanciesIndex.html</A>
</dl>
<DT><BR>
<BR>
<A HREF="S2K.html"><B>Continue to next section</B></A>
<BR>
<BR>
