<H2>THE INCREDIBLE JOURNEY </H2>
 by  Denny Youngs<BR>
<BR>
Hi, my name is Drop.  I was from the air at first.  Until it rained.   I  fell on 
a house and landed in a gutter.  I hit the ground.  Then I was in the ground.  It 
was cool in the ground.   I saw a worm and  a snake.   The snake was thirsty and 
it got me in his belly. He ate a mouse and I got out for once.  Then I went up in the sky and 
came back down in the rain.  Then I fell on a apple and a kid ate the apple.  I know 
I am inside a kid now. He went to the bathroom and now I am in a john.   He flushed 
the john and I went down to the river.   I saw a long thing with a motor.  The thing 
pushed me onto the land.  I went back down into the ground.   I saw a mouse and ran 
so I wouldn't get eaten.  I  know  I ran into a tree's root. I crawled up the tree 
and a bird called Loud Mouth picked me up.  Loud Mouth  took off with me but I fell on a 
plant that sucked me up. I   am hoping I can get out of this plant and go on with 
my journey.   My journey takes me to my birthday, October 18, as I am 500,000,000,002. 
   I AM OLD.<BR><H4 ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="biothree.html">Journal 3</A></H4>

</BODY>
