<H2>THE INCREDIBLE JOURNEY</H2>
<BR>
 by Erica Brayton<BR>
<BR>
This is a story about a water drop named Fred. This story starts 5 million years ago 
when Fred was born.  Today is his 5 million and 1 birthday. It all started when Fred 
was born, he had become a lake and was formed into a water cycle that gets recycled. 
He was transferred through many different places.   It first started when Fred was 
drank by a dinosaur, got washed out of the dinosaur, and went  back into the river. 
When people came down to earth, they started to drink this water and they also drank 
Fred. When these people went to the bathroom, they let Fred out and into the ground. Fred, 
along with his family, got absorbed into the ground and stayed there for a while. 
 When it was time for him to leave again, he went through a system and into a well. 
 Fred got  drank again because he was in the well and got flushed out of  the person's 
body that drank him. And off he went again.   He just kept on going through the same 
thing every time he got drank.   Just like he started from the water cycle, he came 
down as rain,  was drank by someone, and got flushed through someone's body.  Like I 
said, he kept going through the same thing over and over again. Today is the 5 millionth 
and 1 birthday.   Right now he is probably in someone's body (mine maybe) waiting 
to be recycled again and again. <BR><H4 ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="biofour.html">Journal 4</A></H4>

</BODY>
