<BODY>

<H2>THE INCREDIBLE JOURNEY </H2>
 by  Justin Fitzgerald<BR>
<BR>
Once there was a water drop named Billy.  He lived 5 billion years old, long before 
Dinosaurs.   He was recycled more than 5 billion years.  Billy went in a dinosaur 
and out the other side.   He was in and out the other side of every dinosaur alive. 
  Then it started to rain cats and dogs, hurricanes and twisters.  Five billions years 
after the same old thing, humans were made on earth. They made things called wells. 
Billy fell on earth and went into the water system.  He was drank by Bobby, Brian, 
Joe, Moe, and Tina.   Billy went in and out of everyone.  Then he left and went to other 
houses and out of those other houses.  By October 1,  he was at some pioneers cabin. 
 His name was John Dann.   John Dann liked to climb mountains and trees.  One day 
John was thirsty,  so he drank Billy.  Billy went in one way and out the other way.   Up 
to this day,  Billy has been recycled billions of times.   Today Billy is 5 billion 
and 1 years.   Now he hopes he will never be drank again.<BR>
<H4 ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="biofive.html">Journal 5</A></H4>
