<H2>THE INCREDIBLE JOURNEY</H2>
<BR>
 by  Mindy Cole<BR>
<BR>
Hi my name is Yosi  and I 'm a water drop. I've been all over in five billion years. 
When I rained,  I really came pouring down.   I passed a bolt of lightning and went 
down to the ground.   I sat there awhile and then got sucked into the ground.   After 
I traveled to the sewer system.   I left there because it stank.  Then I met Josh, 
the water well.   He gave me a place to stay with my brother J.W.   I was so glad 
to see J.W.  because  I haven't seen him for 2 billion years!  But after I hugged 
him,  I was suddenly being sucked up by something.   I was crying but J.W. said not to worry. 
  "It's just a part of the water cycle".   I was put into a glass with Jenny, Denny, 
and Bobby.   As I looked  harder, I found my boyfriend Andy.   I was ready to talk 
to them when the glass tipped up and out we all went.    About 10 hours later, my cousin, 
Justin, let us all out into a sink which made me end up right where I started!   
 <BR>
