<BODY>
<BR>

<H2>Why is it important to have clean water? </H2>
<STRONG><BR>
</STRONG>
We don't want to catch any diseases that can be in the water.<BR>
You don't drink anything that you are not supposed to.<BR>
<BR>

<H2>Why is it important to know your water is clean? </H2>
<BR>
So you know what you are swimming in and so you know what<BR>
 kind of environment your frogs, salamanders, turtles, etc. are living<BR>
 in.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Steven Parotta<BR>
Denny Young<BR>
Justin Fitzgerald<BR>
Gina Dolan<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

<H2> If the water is clean: </H2>
<STRONG><BR>
</STRONG>
If the water has bacteria in it  and the people drink it  they can get sick (and/or) 
  die. It is important to have clean water so it's good enough to drink and to take 
a  shower. It's important because it's a main water source for animal and plants 
to   live in and to drink.<BR>
<BR>
Erica Kirkpatrick<BR>
Charity LaTray<BR>
Roger Dean<BR>
Brandon Shippee<BR>

