<BR>
<CENTER><B>II.   FACULTY APPOINTMENT AND EMPLOYMENT</B></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>

<dl>
<dt><br>
<A NAME="l><b>L. MANDATORY RETIREMENT </A></b>
<dt><br>
	Mandatory retirement due to age is prohibited by State law for public sector employees including tenured faculty.  Professional staff who wish to retire shall notify, in writing, the President with respect to the effective date of retirement.
<dt><br>
	Members of the professional staff may be retired for mental or physical incapacity which prevents such persons from adequately performing their duties.

</dl>
