<dt><br>
		<dt>SUNY Potsdam is accredited by the Middle States Association of Colleges and Secondary Schools.  The College's Crane School of Music is accredited by the National Association of Schools of Music.  The College's Chemistry Department is accredited by the American Chemical Society.
<dt><br>
	<dt><i><A NAME="9A2">2.	UNDERGRADUATE DEGREE PROGRAMS</A></i>
<dt><br>
		<dt>SUNY Potsdam offers three undergraduate degrees, the Bachelor of Arts, the Bachelor of Science, and the Bachelor of Music.  All are liberal arts based and offer opportunity for professional training.

