<CENTER><a HREF = "http://www.potsdam.edu/HR/HRHomePage/HRindex.html>Human Resources Home Page</A> <!-- Graphic Tag --><IMG WIDTH=8 HEIGHT=8  SRC="http://www.potsdam.edu/hr/faculty_handbook/BL_DIAM.GIF">

