<DOCHDR>
http://www.potsdam.edu:80/EDUC/GLC/river/chem/pednine.html 137.143.111.2 19970209021546 text/html 2996
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/31205
Message-ID: <af0d121d.145062@www.potsdam.edu>
