<BR>

  <center><strong>VIII.  ATTENDANCE AND LEAVE BENEFITS</A></strong></center>
<dt><br>                                

<dd><dl>
<dt><A NAME=8A>A</A>.   <b>DEFINITIONS</b>
                                    
 <dt><br>
<dd><dl>
<dt><!-- Anchor Point Tag --><A NAME="S8A1">1</A>.  <i>CALENDAR YEAR EMPLOYEE</i>
<dt><br>
          <dt>A calendar year employee is any member of the professional staff having a 12-month professional obligation.

     </dl>                                  
 <dt><br>
<dd><dl>
<dt><!-- Anchor Point Tag --><A NAME="2">2</A>.   <i>ACADEMIC YEAR EMPLOYEE</i>
<dt><br>
          <dt>An academic year employee is any member of the professional staff           having an academic year professional obligation.

     </dl>                                  
 <dt><br>
<dd><dl>
<dt><!-- Anchor Point Tag --><A NAME="3">3</A>.   <i>COLLEGE YEAR EMPLOYEE</i>
<dt><br>
          <dt>A college year employee is any member of the professional staff other than an academic year employee having an annual professional obligation of less than 12 months.
</dl>
</dl>  
