<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#0000ff" vlink="#ff00ff">

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=462 HEIGHT=87  SRC="../FACBOOK.GIF"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><strong>IV.  FACULTY COMPENSATION</strong></CENTER> <BR>
<BR>
<dt><br>
<dd><dl>
<dt><strong>L.	<A NAME="L">CREDIT UNION</A></strong>
<dt><br>
Membership in the Adirondack Regional Federal Credit Union, located at 166 Market Street, is available to faculty and staff at the College.  The Credit Union offers share savings accounts, share draft accounts, loans (personal, home improvement, automobile), life insurance, travelers checks, money market certificates, and a Christmas Club program.  Visit their website at  (http://adkcreditunion.com)  or reach them at their e-mail address (arfcu@northweb.com).

</dl>
	<br>
