<DOCHDR>
http://www.potsdam.edu:80/HR/faculty_handbook/Ch3/S3A.html 137.143.111.2 19970209004435 text/html 22025
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/2.0 ID/31205
Message-ID: <af0d121d.144240@www.potsdam.edu>
