 <P><P><P><P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=6><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#084842">Water Quality Reports</FONT></FONT> </B></CENTER><P>
</BODY><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#084842">Welcome to the water quality home page.  Below are links to the data collected on field trips during the first round of field trips from September 1996 to December 1996.  Water samples were collected at the origin of the Oswegatchie in the Adirondack mountains, at three intermediate sites, and at the point where the Oswegatchie ends as it flows into the Saint Lawrence River.</FONT> 
<P>
<center><TABLE border=1 CELLPADDING=2 CELLSPACING=2 WIDTH="80%">
