Journal entry 9/14/96<BR>
Stacey Maguire<BR>
<BR>
I spend a few hours working on this weeks lesson plan. I made up a game for Thursday: 
heavy metals tic tac toe.  I don't like to listen to lectures and don't want to make 
the students do that.  Hopefully the game will go good.<BR>
Have to look for a bigger classroom.  Having 10 of us in this small one tends to make 
me feel claustrophobic.<BR><H4 ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="staceyth.html">Journal 3</A></H4>
