<TITLE>Eric2.html</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
Journal Week 2<BR>
Eric Burke<P>


This week we explained the water testing.  We went through the test kits and covered testing procedures.  We also talked about safety precautions.  We then explained each of the tests; why we test, sources of the things we test for, and their effects on the environment.  We used an overhead and lectured, however encouraging student participation if they already knew something about the testing.  The students did not seem interested and none of them took notes.  I don't think we'll lecture again. <P>

<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="Eric4.html">Journal 2</A>
</BODY>
