<BODY>
Journal Week 4<BR>
Eric Burke<P>


This week our test site was in Fine.  I had a very difficult time keeping the students on track.  I think it's because our group was able to see the biology group across the river and became preoccupied with what they were doing.  We were done early so we allowed the students some time to explore.  They really enjoyed this time and maybe 
we can use it in the future as a reward for staying on task.<P>

