<BODY>
Journal Week 5<BR>
Eric Burke<P>


We tested at two sites this week and the students did exceptionally well.  We were able to finish both sites with time to spare.  They are all still eager to participate in the testing and, for the most part, are able to do the testing with little instruction.  We filled out the water quality index sheets in the field this week.  They do not like doing these, yet they are anxious to get the results of the water testing.<P>

<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="Eric6.html">Journal 4</A>

