<BR>
Journal Week 6<BR>
Eric Burke<P>


We finished our last test site this week and spent Thursday preparing the students for their lab practical.  They were not at all interested in this preparation, despite knowing the practical was the next day.  I can only hope that they will remember from their field experience.  From what I have observed, I am confident they know how to perform the tests they can do well on this exam.<P>

