I made study guides for Ch. 2, 3 (my tests) and 4.  I haven't heard from Tyna so I am assuming that we are a "Go" on the midterm.  She was asking Mike to run off the chapters.  I'm going to try and fax the guides to Gouverneur tomorrow morning.<P>


