Journal 10/7<BR>
Stacey Maguire<P>


I faxed the study guides to Gouverneur for Tyna. <P>


I'm in the process of putting all site data on the MAC for the Weeb.  I have 2 sites from last week to go.  It is taking me so long to save the data for some reason. Old computers.<P>


Dr. Doody gave me the new batteries for the TDS tester today.  Yeh!  The students love to do that test.  Part of the reason is probably because we call it our "Pocket Pal".   They all seem to think that's funny.<P>

