Journal 10/8<BR>
Stacey Maguire<P>


Talked to Tyna after class tonight.  Things have been hectic at Gouverneur.  We are a "go" for the midterm however.  Mike is going to give out the study guides and copies of the chapters today.<P>


I have to remember to tell them tomorrow that the study guides should be done for our review on Thursday.  <P>


We've been talking more about the midterm.  Tyna will grade the exam as Eric and I wrote most of it.  Each part will count 50 points with a 100pt total possible.<P>

